HEADWORD: Electro-gilding
<hw>E*lec`tro-gild"ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The art or
process of gilding copper, iron, etc., by means of voltaic
electricity.</def>⟦br⟧
